content: This spiritbox does work pretty good. You will need to let spirits have time to learn how to use it so keep it running for a little bit. I've gotten intelligent replies with this one.

Apart from the static being too loud I found this app the best one yet. It said my name within a minute of starting it. Was getting intelligent responses, I asked for my dads name and it came through. Then what he drank and it said whiskey, then dram which is a Scottish word for a drink. So many others that's too long to write but I highly recommend this app. Can the static be sorted though it's far too loud
